EASTERN MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
EGYPT.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY IN PROGRESS UNTIL 04 SEP
   BY M/V PACIFIC EXPLORER TOWING SIX
   8400 METER LONG CABLES IN AREA BETWEEN
   31-35N 31-51N AND 031-32E 032-20E.

2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1899/12.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 05 SEP 12.
